window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Some doors should not be opened.&nbsp;</p> <p>Some can never be closed.&nbsp;</p> <p>Jo Palmer’s peaceful and happy life is about to end.&nbsp;</p> <p>Ash - the man she loves - will be arrested by the police.&nbsp;</p> <p>Millie - her precious daughter - will be taken from her.&nbsp;</p> <p>She will lose her friends.&nbsp;</p> <p>She will doubt her sanity.&nbsp;</p> <p>Someone is stealing everything Jo loves, and will stop at nothing.&nbsp;</p> <p>But right now, Jo is laughing in her kitchen, eating dinner with her family, suspecting nothing.&nbsp;</p> <p>It’s raining outside.&nbsp;</p> <p>There’s a knock at the door. They are here.&nbsp;</p> <p>A DCI Tom Douglas Thriller.</p>"; 
